Introduction to Collaboration

Collaboration sites make it easier and more efficient to work together in teams.

They fulfil the need for departments to gather important documents and information arround tasks,

actions, and planning effortlessly accross country and organizational borders. We offer several tools

when collaborating. One Drive, Teams and SharePoint Online find out more
